videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham discusses being tasked with the challenge of guarding Buddy Hield and leading the Jayhawks to a road win against the Sooners.
videos.headline: Graham: I took it personal

videos.description: Dan Shulman and Jay Bilas break down Devonte' Graham's big performance in scoring 27 points for Kansas while keeping Oklahoma's Buddy Hield in check.
videos.headline: Graham's big game key to Kansas win

videos.description: Rece Davis, Jay Williams and Seth Greenberg discuss the Jayhawks' 76-72 win over the Sooners which featured some questionable calls from the referees.
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown with Rece Davis, Jay Williams, and Seth Greenberg

videos.description: After being held without a field goal in the first half, Oklahoma G Buddy Hield goes off in the second half connecting on five 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Hield's second half 3-point explosion

videos.description: Devonte' Graham kept Buddy Hield in check as he led the Jayhawks to a 76-72 win over Oklahoma.
